=== GHOST_WHALE_SONG ===
# id: 99
# title: The Ghost Whale's Song
# chinese_title: 鬼鲸之歌
# category: Creature
# mode: dungeon

Deep vibrations shake the station — the song of a ghost whale, a spectral leviathan that inhabits the spaces between dimensions. Its form is visible only as a shimmer against the stars, a shape so vast it dwarfs the station. The song carries alien emotions: curiosity, ancient sadness, and something that feels like recognition.

* [Sing back — match the vibration pattern]
  ~ gain_radical("鬼")
  "鬼" (guǐ) — ghost, spirit, phantom
* [Record the ghost whale's song]
  ~ gain_xp(25)
  "鲸" (jīng) — whale
* [Open yourself to the alien emotions]
  ~ gain_radical("心")
  "魂" (hún) — soul, spirit. Contains the radical "鬼."
* [Observe from a safe distance]
  ~ gain_xp(15)
  "观" (guān) — to observe, to watch
